message: Dear Bob, I am delighted to present our flagship product, which I believe would greatly benefit you and add significant value to your endeavors. Given its worth and the impact it could have on your projects, I am offering it to you at an exclusive price of $9,500. This is a special opportunity to acquire a product that is valued at $10,000, but with a slight discount to ensure you receive the best deal possible. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further or if there's anything else I can assist you with.
